Package multidendrograms.initial

Class InitialProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • multidendrograms.initial.InitialProperties
  • public class InitialProperties
extends java.lang.Object

    MultiDendrograms

    It defines all the parameters of the application and it initializes them with the values in the file md.ini, or with default values if the file is missing
    Since:
    JDK 6.0
    Author:
    Justo Montiel, David Torres, Sergio Gómez, Alberto Fernández
